{"tid":1908562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"接載湖北港人首班專機暫定明午抵港　第二班晚上8時半","createTime":"2020-03-03T11:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T11:20:53.000Z","uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"953cbaf52ae82b42473720beed1f345656370596","tid":1908562,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:10:03.000Z","msg":"政府宣布明天（4日）和後天（5日）將有4班專機赴武漢，接載主要在湖北武漢的港人返港。兩日的航班暫定分別約下午4時半及8時半抵港，返港的人會隨即送往駿洋邨作檢疫。港府安排40多人團隊赴武漢機場處理手續，包括政制及內地事務局長聶德權、政治助理吳璟儁等，並將最少有17名醫護人員隨團。<br />\n<br />\n在武漢港人今日收到入境處信息，指出為減低傳染病風險，武漢天河國際機場和專機不會提供任何餐飲，建議離開住所前在家用膳、徹底洗澡洗頭，並用熱水和家用洗衣液或消毒劑徹底清洗會穿的衣物。返港者所攜行李應盡量輕便，信息並附上航空公司有關行李要求。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早表示，第一批回港者共有533人。滯留武漢660港人中，有440人會乘坐包機，而在武漢市以外的地區，會優先處理比較緊急的個案，第一類是孕婦；第二類是患病者，他們需要回港接受治療或手術；第三類是需要回港應考文憑試（DSE）的畢業生，有93人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200303/s00005/1583231625051/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%8e%a5%e8%bc%89%e6%b9%96%e5%8c%97%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e9%a6%96%e7%8f%ad%e5%b0%88%e6%a9%9f%e6%9a%ab%e5%ae%9a%e6%98%8e%e5%8d%88%e6%8a%b5%e6%b8%af-%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e7%8f%ad%e6%99%9a%e4%b8%8a8%e6%99%82%e5%8d%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200303%2Fs00005%2F1583231625051%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%258e%25a5%25e8%25bc%2589%25e6%25b9%2596%25e5%258c%2597%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e9%25a6%2596%25e7%258f%25ad%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%25a9%259f%25e6%259a%25ab%25e5%25ae%259a%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%258d%2588%25e6%258a%25b5%25e6%25b8%25af-%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e7%258f%25ad%25e6%2599%259a%25e4%25b8%258a8%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%258d%258a&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=ae42bcd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200303%2Fs00005%2F1583231625051%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%258e%25a5%25e8%25bc%2589%25e6%25b9%2596%25e5%258c%2597%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e9%25a6%2596%25e7%258f%25ad%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%25a9%259f%25e6%259a%25ab%25e5%25ae%259a%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%258d%2588%25e6%258a%25b5%25e6%25b8%25af-%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e7%258f%25ad%25e6%2599%259a%25e4%25b8%258a8%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%258d%258a&h=3d52bde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200303/s00005/1583231625051/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%8e%a5%e8%bc%89%e6%b9%96%e5%8c%97%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e9%a6%96%e7%8f%ad%e5%b0%88%e6%a9%9f%e6%9a%ab%e5%ae%9a%e6%98%8e%e5%8d%88%e6%8a%b5%e6%b8%af-%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e7%8f%ad%e6%99%9a%e4%b8%8a8%e6%99%82%e5%8d%8a</a>"},{"pid":"809a419bf0365648da8d4835a02461d3c2043235","tid":1908562,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"真係接？<br />\n搞港獨？<br />\n定運埋其他大陸人黎香港"},{"pid":"13e29d7c634d1c45103350644c053ffef22188e1","tid":1908562,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"809a419bf0365648da8d4835a02461d3c2043235","tid":1908562,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"真係接？<br />\n搞港獨？<br />\n定運埋其他大陸人黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"係都唔奇 台灣接嗰堆都同名單上唔同"}]}